description: I'm a family nurse practitioner with a Master's degree from Vanderbilt University, bringing over a decade of diverse nursing experience. Licensed in 33 States. For the past 5 years, I've specialized in telemedicine, offering on-demand urgent care and consultations for a range of conditions across all age groups.
detailOrQuote: With a profound passion for compassionate care, I am dedicated to providing efficient and empathetic healthcare services through telemedicine, ensuring patients receive the highest level of support and attention they deserve.
